A RESOLUTION
1 Recognizing and commending Dr. Jayne Morgan; and for other purposes.
2 WHEREAS, Dr. Jayne Morgan currently serves as vice president of medical affairs at Hello
3 Heart, specializing in women's health and AI; and
4 WHEREAS, recognized by Midi Health's 45 over 45 list of top women's health experts and
5 Atlanta's Most Powerful Leaders in 2024, Dr. Morgan is a leading advocate for improved
6 research and representation in clinical trials of women and all populations; and
7 WHEREAS, with expertise in cardiovascular research, she previously served as executive
8 director of health and community education at Piedmont Healthcare, where she led initiatives
9 such as the Covid Task Force and the Cardiovascular Research Program; and
10 WHEREAS, she is the creator of the award-winning Stairwell Chronicles series and serves
11 as a medical expert for CNN, News Nation, NYC Fox News, and other media outlets, in
12 addition to hosting HealthyHer, a women's health talk show; and
13 WHEREAS, beyond her clinical work, she holds leadership roles on multiple medical boards
14 and committees, contributing to advancements in cardiac care and health literacy; and
